Author: FeiThrowaway
Text: I needed this so much, thank you.  Much love.  ❤️ ❤️

Author: alissajay2
Text: It is the holidays and you deserve to celebrate this limited time of the year like anyone else would. And you won't be able to make cookies at your parents house forever and your body was asking you for those cookies and you deserved them. And you are no weaker or less valuable of a human being for that. Sending so much love.
